    "description_long": "This is a classic, upright fire hydrant with a glossy red finish, featuring a domed top and a cylindrical body. The hydrant has three prominent hose connection outlets: two on the sides and one facing forward, each with a round cap. The base is wide and circular, with bolt holes for secure mounting to the ground. The top of the hydrant is fitted with an operating nut or cap, used for opening the water valve. The surface is smooth and metallic, with no visible manufacturer markings or attached chains.",
